Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.35,0:01:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ルンバ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バシサイヨ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ナイダ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青辣椒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:47.57,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,436)}<Jalapeno>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有着这样的过去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再 再怎么说也太...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:01:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假了点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 姐姐大人 这肯定是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我熟人的朋友也是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 都写在网上了 肯定是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于Sleeping啥的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.37,0:02:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面说美国大兵做宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 是防卫过当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:20.84,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧～对吧～对吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好好好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:25.81,*title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(200,10)}10cm的距離是有意義的！你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃紫叶酱菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:38.28,*title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(345,10)\fs19}看了下久違的原neta 原來當時腮幫子那麼大啊 {\1c&H4D81DF}不過年輕的時候 完全沒放在心上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从上述的事情上看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学园都市进行的能力开发课程当中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:45.54,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(568,438)}<Curriculum>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是 Personal Reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单地来说明的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面放着一只活猫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开盒子之时 猫会是什么状态呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天 你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么死了 要么没死...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎样呢 开盒！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:17.49,*title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(411,10)\fs25}雖然都覺得這個neta要用膩了{\1c&H4D81DF} 但這麼可愛 忍不住又拿出來用了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SF 复活！复活～复活～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干完活喝一杯 实在太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 尽情烤来吃咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作能力差的警备员 没有吃肉的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会发生窝囊废吃不着肉这种惨事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟这可是豪华绚烂烤肉套餐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萌老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就尽情烤 尽情吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉川老师 请帮我拿调味汁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 是酱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到烤肉的调味汁 只有酱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举双手同意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为黄泉川老师喜欢「酱」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不只是调味汁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到动作影星 就是让·克劳德·范达美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.83,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(542,438)}<Jean-Claude Van Damme>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到喜欢发面的少年 就是约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.78,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<neta: 不可思议之海的娜迪娅的男主角>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到麻将 就是电脑麻将
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.61,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<neta: ADK公司1981年5月发售的麻将游戏>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原始森林还有冉·阿让
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:22.33,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(510,436)}<Jean Valjean>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:22.33,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<neta: 悲惨世界/孤星泪的男主角>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 我喜欢的东西全都有个jyan音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还陆续有来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绘画有让·科克托
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:27.88,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(470,438)}<Jean Cocteau>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理有秋山酱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:29.21,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<neta: 漫画铁锅之酱的男主角>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫画有Jump
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.29,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<neta: 周刊少年Jump>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝茶还去Jean-Paul Hevin
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:32.46,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<neta: 用法国巧克力鬼才的名字做的店名>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:34.70,*title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(415,10)}就我個人來說 還是喜歡金龍 不過{\1c&H4D81DF}為了neta... 說來最近都沒看范達美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风车、荷兰、还是德国？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了一群荷兰人穿着裙子走在歌舞伎一条街！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这学园都市啊 不是有超多风车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些风车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有在发电吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在荷兰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有那么多风车哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人你又来了 为什么要说这事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在全日本随便建的风力发电风车要面临被拆的命运哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那些风车 都有在好好转啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是风车啊 是风车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是学园都市啊 学园都市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠这些破风车发电 哪里够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 在内陆会吹风吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有在好好转？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是山背风吧 是在吹山背风吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 我想过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些风车说不定是靠电力转动 而不是用来发电的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人...请不要说傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚自己在说什么啊 黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座都市 绝对有些什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴谋？ 国家秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:06:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风车是国家级的秘密计划啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的假说是正确的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移居火星计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ExMARS Project的一部分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到网上有这个帖子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也听说过这个谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 只有被选中的人类才能逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个无能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:23.68,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(482,438)}<Level 0>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 光靠人类 能实行这个计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球外生命体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是Grey吧 Grey
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.63,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<这里的Grey不是指颜色 而是人们对罗兹威尔事件里面外星人的称呼>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
